Thrust - attack skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Like slice, a thrust is a single direct attack, aiming to
dispatch an opponent who is already at death's door. Rather
than making a crude swing at an enemy, a thrusting attack
is precise and requires greater concentration. By using
finesse instead of brute force, the swashbuckler will find
that larger opponents will fall to his blade. Opponents
that are not near death will still be able to twist away
from a thrusting attack though, taking much less damage than
intended, and will be very wary of any future moved by any
swashbuckler.

GL:  8
SP: 40
command: sthrust <target> (defaults to opponent if in combat)
duration: instant
